data.value: K-Browser is a web browser for Microsoft Windows platform who uses the Trident rendering engine of IE, it is made for easy usage and safe browsing. This application is designed to provide you with a nice interface. It has: a Download manager, Shortcut key commands, Zoom UI, Bookmarks, History Viewer, Cookie Viewer, Rss Reader, Social network Integration, Popup Blocker and a Anti-Phishing Tool.
